overview: Coach follows Tracy Hamm in her quest to earn the internationally renowned UEFA A coaching license. Hamm turned to Europe after her efforts to pursue a top license from U.S. Soccer were obstructed by requirements that candidates seeking waivers to bypass lower certification levels must have played three years of professional soccer. tagline: Coach tells the story of Tracy Hamm's pursuit to obtain the coveted UEFA A-license for football (soccer)
title: Coach
